data.description: Welcome to 11716 Inverness Way in the beautiful Lake of the Pines, California. This updated 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom home is set on half an acre with a private swimming pool, offering a modern and comfortable lifestyle.  The house has been thoughtfully updated with all new high-end windows and sliders, a new HVAC system, and fresh exterior paint. The open floor plan and abundant natural light create an inviting atmosphere. The modern kitchen with newer appliances and the cozy living room with a fireplace are perfect for entertaining.  Step outside to your private oasis, with deck views of the pool and a peek of the lake. Newly installed sprinkler system and lawn. The large primary bedroom features a sitting room with a cozy gas fireplace and slider to the deck and pool. In addition, the house is equipped with a convenient new whole house vacuum system including an attachment in the garage for car cleaning. This property is meticulously maintained and offers an excellent opportunity for comfortable living.  LOP is a gated community with many activities for all ages. Lake life includes golf, pickleball, bocce ball, and family events.
